WEBVTT

00:00.031 --> 00:01.819
Previously on Underground...

00:02.102 --> 00:03.852
The thing's worth more
than your life, boy!

00:03.855 --> 00:05.154
It's my fault... if anybody

00:05.190 --> 00:07.190
gonna be punished, it's gonna be me...

00:07.225 --> 00:09.409
Boy's of age on to becoming a man.

00:09.444 --> 00:11.693
Now would be a good time
for his father to be here.

00:11.696 --> 00:13.696
Everything happened so fast.

00:13.748 --> 00:14.781
I never gave any thought

00:14.833 --> 00:16.449
as to how our new roles

00:16.501 --> 00:17.583
would affect our everyday lives.

00:17.619 --> 00:18.701
You sold my wife.

00:18.703 --> 00:20.670
You think you're
better than me, don't you?

00:20.705 --> 00:21.587
...gal stick her nose up at me.

00:25.176 --> 00:26.542
Come on, we gotta run!

00:26.544 --> 00:27.710
He dead.

