00:40.892 --> 00:42.240
Mr. Bill?

00:47.899 --> 00:49.591
Time to get on up now.

01:42.954 --> 01:44.651
Bill? You in there?

01:46.207 --> 01:47.173
Help! Help!

01:47.208 --> 01:48.758
We need some help in here!

